## Description {#details}

This class contains meta information specific to a module.

Queries can be made by different debugging and exception handling schemes and reformated for specific use.

Definition at line 82 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/codegen/machinemoduleinfo-h">MachineModuleInfo.h</a>.
